data.description:
New photos coming - main level has been painted light and bright French Grey! BRING AN OFFER and your personal touch to this priced-to-sell property! Motivated sellers. This is a TON of space on an amazing lot in Olathe! A beautiful and spacious home close to everything WITH a 3 car garage! Situated on a cozy cul-de-sac and away from the main road, this former model home will welcome you inside to a stunning two-story entry. New fencing to enclose the large backyard with room to get creative, and plenty of additional space in the finished basement.
The main level flows with an open concept and light-filled living, eat-in kitchen, and living. View the backyard from the kitchen sink, where storage abounds and there is plenty of workspace. Easily access either the dining room OR eat-in kitchen with this logical layout. The living room offers room for various furniture arrangements and wall space for a TV suited for movie night.
Upstairs leads you through French doors to the generous primary suite. The grand primary bath holds TWO walk-in closets, large shower, soaking tub, and soaring vaulted ceilings. A conveniently located laundry room is adjacent to the primary and accessed from the hallway. Bedroom 2 has a private en suite, and bedroom 3 and 4 share a Hollywood bath.
The finished basement offers space to get creative, with a full bath, ADDITIONAL washer/dryer hookups, and natural light.
This fantastic home is just a short distance to Arbor Landing Park, with large and small play structures, resistance equipment, picnic shelter and walking loop!
Less than a minute drive to Starbucks, Price Chopper and plenty of new storefronts and restaurants! 
This home is just WAITING for YOUR vision and personal touch!
